OL,3,CWoman who fractured skull in motorbike
OL,4,Ccrash on road to recovery
OL,6,FA woman who fractured her skull as
OL,7,Fwell as breaking numerous bones whilst
OL,8,Friding her motorbike in Cumbria has
OL,9,Fran a half marathon for charity.
OL,11,FRuth Cork was riding her motorbike on
OL,12,Fthe A65 near with her friend, who was
OL,13,Fon a separate bike, when she was
OL,14,Finvolved in a collision with a car.
OL,16,FThe crash happened on 19 August 2022
OL,17,Fwith Ruth having no memory of the
OL,18,Fincident.
