OL,3,CWoman who fractured skull in motorbike
OL,4,Ccrash on road to recovery
OL,6,FRuth had broken several bones
OL,7,Fincluding her femur, sacrum, jaw,
OL,8,Fzygoma, skull and pelvis.
OL,10,FShe also had a bleed to the brain and
OL,11,Fdisplaced and crushed a few vertebrae.
OL,13,FThe Great North Air Ambulance Service
OL,14,F(GNAAS) flew to the scene and took
OL,15,FRuth to the Royal Preston Hospital.
OL,17,FRuth said: "My recovery has been long
OL,18,Fand challenging, but I've had a lot of
OL,19,Fhelp through it.
