OL,3,CWoman who fractured skull in motorbike
OL,4,Ccrash on road to recovery
OL,6,F"On the major trauma ward the nurses
OL,7,Fwere fantastic, the doctors were
OL,8,Fbrilliant and the physios at Preston
OL,9,Fgot me standing up, and then when I
OL,10,Ftransferred to Stanford Hall, we did a
OL,11,Flot more work with hydrotherapy and
OL,12,Fphysio work to get me back to a state
OL,13,Fof walking.
OL,15,F"It's been a progression from zimmer
OL,16,Fframe to crutches to stick to then
OL,17,Fhaving no aids at all."
