OL,6,FRuth had initially planned to run the
OL,7,FShrewsbury Half Marathon but due to
OL,8,Fher injuries she pushed it back to the
OL,9,Ffollowing year.
OL,11,FShe said: "I was still not technically
OL,12,Fat the point of running, so I decided
OL,13,FI would walk, but my competitive
OL,14,Fstreak got ahead of me.
OL,16,F"So a slow jog, walk, run type thing
OL,17,Fhappened and 13.1 miles later I
OL,18,Fcompleted it."
