OL,6,FRuth decided to run the half marathon
OL,7,Fto raise funds for the GNAAS and
OL,8,Fdonated more than #1,000.
OL,10,FShe said: "There were a lot of people
OL,11,Fthat helped me on the route of my
OL,12,Frecovery and it was Preston that saved
OL,13,Fmy life at the time, but I wouldn't
OL,14,Fhave got there if it hadn't been for .
OL,16,F"I think if I had to transfer by road,
OL,17,Fthere was a chance that I might not
OL,18,Fhave quite got there."
