OL,6,FRuth is now back riding her bike and
OL,7,Fhas set her sights on volunteering for
OL,8,Fthe Blood Bikes.
OL,10,FShe said: "I am back on a bike,
OL,11,Funfortunately for some people, but
OL,12,Fthat's what I find a zest for life in,
OL,13,Fand the aim now is to become a blood
OL,14,Fbiker, to give something back to that
OL,15,Fas well."
